classifications.author: EcoFeministWarrior3000

classifications.author: ReproductiveRevolution

The language used ('fiercely defend,' 'blatant attack') reflects the urgency and moral framing typical of left-wing advocacy on reproductive rights, contrasting with conservative efforts to restrict abortion. No references to traditional values, religious arguments, or fetal rights—common in right-wing discourse—are present.
